 ('1', '1', 'en_ca', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-09-26 20:51:47', '2015-12-09 21:00:51', '5067ca9b-e4f8-47f5-8e65-89aa43f4abbf'),
 ('2', '2', 'en_ca', 'Konnexis', '<p>It’s true, this site doesn’t have a whole lot of content yet, but don’t worry. Our web developers have just installed the CMS, and they’re setting things up for the content editors this very moment. Soon Konnexis.dev will be an oasis of fresh perspectives, sharp analyses, and astute opinions that will keep you coming back again and again.</p>', 'Global Market Leaders in Sterilization Control and Monitoring Systems', 'Advanced monitoring solutions designed for the sterilization industry, for growth, production efficiency and the long term.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-09-26 20:51:48', '2015-12-30 17:03:14', '6a7e834e-4619-423d-a8fe-a60013784d76'),
 ('3', '3', 'en_ca', 'We just installed Craft!', '<p>Craft is the CMS that’s powering Konnexis.dev. It’s beautiful, powerful, flexible, and easy-to-use, and it’s made by Pixel & Tonic. We can’t wait to dive in and see what it’s capable of!</p><!--pagebreak--><p>This is even more captivating content, which you couldn’t see on the News index page because it was entered after a Page Break, and the News index template only likes to show the content on the first page.</p><p>Craft: a nice alternative to Word, if you’re making a website.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-09-26 20:51:49', '2015-10-03 23:14:07', '92cc1d6a-2e07-4253-b7d9-db2d9584e878'),
 ('4', '4', 'en_ca', 'Home Header', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-10-03 15:07:35', '2015-10-03 15:07:49', '83f48ce3-98d1-496a-a1b0-bbae3664ece7'),
 ('5', '5', 'en_ca', 'Medical Device Manufacturers', NULL, NULL, 'Konnexis helps you ensure that your products are efficiently and properly sterilized through integration of data management systems in Irradiator and chamber control. Our systems include product tracking, specification management, and process monitoring. We offer seamless integration with our customers’ MRP systems, providing enterprise-wide access to on-the-floor information in real time.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-10-03 15:33:54', '2015-10-12 19:44:17', 'e80f4875-5b5f-4f87-a2cd-9cdbe7be10d7'),
 ('6', '6', 'en_ca', 'Sterilization Services Contractors', NULL, NULL, 'Many sterilization service contractors work hand-in-hand with medical device manufacturers. We recognize this, so we have developed our sterilization control systems to improve this partnership. Cycles can be easily imported/exported through email, improving communication between contractors and manufacturers. By providing affordable scalability to sterilization service contractors, our software gives you the competitive edge you need to improve your performance in the industry.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-10-03 15:34:10', '2015-12-29 18:57:43', '1a99290f-dfdc-423b-a959-08f0490e2b06'),
 ('7', '7', 'en_ca', 'Products & Services', NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-10-03 15:34:32', '2015-10-17 18:46:39', 'c4baed94-17d5-4434-844f-cbe337495423'),
 ('8', '8', 'en_ca', 'AccuSOLO', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-10-03 15:34:54', '2015-10-18 01:38:40', 'f319c3de-b911-4344-8577-273965a512d2'),
 ('9', '9', 'en_ca', 'konnTRACK', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-10-03 15:35:41', '2015-10-17 19:44:46', '5bbc0382-bb66-485e-b08d-3ab1db7425c9'),
 ('10', '10', 'en_ca', 'Consulting Services', NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-10-03 15:36:12', '2015-10-17 19:44:56', 'b1424b83-24c4-44c0-a951-3cc72020a97b'),
 ('11', '11', 'en_ca', 'Sterilization Methods', NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-10-03 15:36:28', '2015-12-30 17:23:38', '31cbe06e-1ba4-4b85-8960-dc482e780a0c'),
 ('12', '12', 'en_ca', 'Help Desk', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-10-03 15:36:40', '2015-10-03 15:36:40', 'c5d50888-e132-42e3-a5fc-75cd9db028c7'),
 ('13', '13', 'en_ca', 'About Us', NULL, NULL, 'Originally from Slovakia, Peter Veselovsky came to Canada to study process engineering at the University of Toronto. As an avid skier he fell in love with Canadian winters and decided to stay. While working with Nordion leading their Irradiator Control Systems group and their Radiation Therapy Controls group he realized that the level of integration into large company systems was severely lacking. Peter believed that it was possible to integrate sterilization control systems with manufacturer’s complex work flows and still have highly effective and safe systems that would meet stringent regulatory standards. With this aim, Peter formed Konnexis in 2000 and now, with his hand picked team, provides control systems and integration services for sterilization systems of all kinds around the world.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-10-03 15:36:49', '2015-10-18 16:30:49', '4cc639ce-af66-4c6a-b5a6-c36f973da0c3'),
 ('14', '14', 'en_ca', 'Ron Nyegard', '<p>Konnexis continues to provide excellent consulting, system development, and end-user support services to STERIS Isomedix Services. With over a 6-year business relationship, we have used Konnexis resources for development and implementation of our ERP application, business-to-business web services, customer web portal, and various process control and monitoring systems for both gamma and ethylene oxide processing. Their system’s expertise has delivered innovative solutions to our business requirements, resulting in positive impacts on our daily operations and our overall customer satisfaction ratings.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Director of Operations Systems Development at STERIS Isomedix Services', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-10-03 18:33:38', '2015-10-03 18:33:38', 'a36a794e-ec58-4b28-a9e0-5ec23c1a0d7d'),
 ('15', '15', 'en_ca', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'sales@konnexis.com', '1-613-599-7371', '300 March Road, Suite 102, Kanata, ON K2K 2E2', 'https://twitter.com/Konnexis', 'http://www.linkedin.com/company/konnexis', '2015-10-03 18:37:49', '2015-12-30 16:44:01', 'e03dbc54-1d2e-499b-a41c-00765e8aca84'),
 ('16', '16', 'en_ca', 'Kitchen Sink', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-10-03 21:26:13', '2015-10-03 21:26:13', 'b3890c6d-5d5a-4672-be10-8bf87d53090f'),
 ('17', '17', 'en_ca', 'Integrated Control Systems', '<p>Konnexis’ control systems do more than simply monitor your sterilization process.  This is because our systems are fully integrated with product tracking and process monitoring!  Read <a title=\"Why Konnexis?\" href=\"http://www.konnexis.com/why-integrate/\">About Us&gt;&gt;Why Konnexis?</a> to find out about the benefits of our systems.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-10-03 22:39:22', '2015-10-03 23:08:41', 'e34a107e-8150-4ee7-af0d-2feeef542223'),
