 ('62', '2', '1', '57', 'en_ca', '11', 'updates to About us intro based on GDoc', '{\"typeId\":\"1\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Konnexis\",\"slug\":\"homepage\",\"postDate\":1445093378,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"fields\":{\"5\":[\"4\"],\"7\":{\"28\":{\"type\":\"textWithPhoto\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"backgroundColor\":\"white\",\"sectionHeading\":\"Global Market Leaders\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Peter Veselovsky recognized the need for an expert in sterilization software, and Konnexis Inc. was created to meet this need. As a global market leader in sterilization control systems, Konnexis Inc. remains dedicated to the sterilization industry, providing future-proof control systems for sterilizers across the globe.<\\/p>\",\"callToActionText\":\"About\",\"callToActionLink\":[\"13\"],\"photo\":[\"33\"],\"photoAlignment\":\"right\"}},\"29\":{\"type\":\"previewTiles\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"pages\":[\"5\",\"6\"],\"tileType\":\"overlay\"}},\"35\":{\"type\":\"tabList\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"tabListTitle\":\"Sterilization Methods\",\"tabs\":{\"36\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"tabTitle\":\"Ethylene Oxide\",\"tabIcon\":\"oxide\",\"tabContent\":\"Konnexis is a leader in the design of control systems for ethylene oxide chambers. Konnexis takes your specifications into account and implements a control system which increases efficiency, functionality, and productivity. Integrating both flexibility and precision into your system, AccuSOLO is Konnexis\' most advanced solution for process control.\"}},\"37\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"tabTitle\":\"Gamma Irradiation\",\"tabIcon\":\"gamma\",\"tabContent\":\"Konnexis has developed a system for Gamma and E-Beam irradiators that is highly flexible in order to both suit your needs and to accommodate for the changing industry. Through seamless integration between irradiator control and product tracking, Konnexis has allowed its Gamma irradiation customers to reach unparalleled levels of productivity.