 ('4', '25', 'en_ca', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '<h2>Dedicated to the Sterilization Industry</h2><p>Konnexis Inc. provides process control systems specifically for the sterilization industry delivering advanced and expert control and monitoring solutions for growth, production efficiency, and a future-proof system. Since 2000, Konnexis Inc. has grown to establish an international presence within the sterilization industry partnering with some of the world’s largest <a href=\"{entry:6:url}\">contract sterilization companies</a> and <a href=\"{entry:5:url}\">medical device manufacturers</a>.\r\n</p>', '<h2>Global Market Leaders in Sterilization Control Systems</h2><p>Konnexis is a global market leader of modern sterilization control systems. We have a range of proven solutions that have undergone rigorous testing to provide you with a reliable and dependable solution for any sterilization modality. Konnexis was selected as the control system for the world’s first high volume industrial sterilization x-ray facility. Our control systems are being used throughout the world which <strong>sterilize over 1 million pallets per year.</strong>\r\n</p>', 'white', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-10-12 19:42:29', '2015-10-18 16:30:49', '6f7a3ff3-3dc3-41ae-b9eb-f84289dda18f'),
