 ('7', '28', 'en_ca', 'white', 'Global Market Leaders', '<p>Peter Veselovsky recognized the need for an expert in sterilization software, and Konnexis Inc. was created to meet this need. As a global market leader in sterilization control systems, Konnexis Inc. remains dedicated to the sterilization industry, providing future-proof control systems for sterilizers across the globe.\r\n</p>', 'About', 'right', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-10-17 14:50:53', '2015-12-30 17:03:14', '619e363d-d386-49e9-8b87-8cc280000290'),
