 ('18', '45', 'en_ca', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'konnTRACK', '<p>konnTRACK seamlessly integrates your sterilization machine with process control and inventory tracking. Developed with vision, this software operates with X-Ray, Gamma and E-Beam technologies.  By advancing plant efficiency, minimizing downtown, and with unparalleled reliability in scheduling, konnTRACK is definitive in increasing production. </p>', 'white', '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-10-17 19:37:57', '2015-10-17 19:44:46', 'dc775435-8a65-4bc7-a94a-b5353c268f3b'),
