 ('20', '47', 'en_ca', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, 'Full Lifecycle Support with Fastest Deployment', 'When partnering with Konnexis, our team of experts will support you through the whole system integration process; from project planning and management to post installation support. We have our own quality management systems experts to assist customers with audits. We provide assistance through:', '2015-10-18 02:16:12', '2015-10-18 16:30:49', '6ae0e0d1-dbea-4230-a0cf-9f63eaa408e1'),
